frame of my scepter in my current weakened state. I need a soul to regain my pow...&quot; quickly hand in your Emerald Essence.<br><br>5) You have one more line where you will ask the spirit, &quot;what frame of your scepter?&quot; and the spirit will hand you Sceptre of Akelha Ra Frame, a 10 slot container.<br><br>6) Now you will need to gather the 10 Luclin Shards for the container. They are located in these zones on the following mobs as rare drops. Individually they will identify as different letters of the Akhevan alphabet:<br>- Fungus Grove on Shik`Nar Warriors, Soldiers, and Royals (Dat)<br>- Scarlet Desert on Sun Revenants and Reavers (Set)<br>- The Deep on Thought Leeches or Thought Horrors (Raf)<br>- The Grey on Sun Revenants (Kel)<br>- Dawnshroud Peaks on Rockhoppers (Lor)<br>- Akheva Ruins on Xi Vius, Shadow Reavers, and Shade Golems (Dax)<br>- Ssraeashza Temple on any skeleton (Vin)<br>- Maiden's Eye on Goranga Foragers, Gathers, Hunters, Prophets, and Seers (Tak)<br>- Acrylia Caverns on Grimling Skullcrackers (Ved)<br>- Sanctus Seru on A Legionnaire of the Hand (Kelera)<br><br>7) Combine the items and you will reassemble the Scepter. It is now a 2 slot container item.<br><br> The 2 items you need for the container are the Glowing Orb of Luclinite, dropped by any high-level Luclin encounter, and a Shaded Sphere that is summoned by a staff that drops off the Emperor Ssraeshza. Combine the Glowing Orb of Luclinite and the Shaded Sphere summoned by the Emperor's staff and you will receive your key to Vex Thal, the Scepter of Shadows.  <p> <a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=209283 >Sonicbeat the Virtuoso</a><br>Hater of Kirsta<br> Leader of Team Rawr </p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/uraiyaeq.showPublicProfile?language=EN>RaiyaEQ</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Contributing Member</span><br>  Posts: 461<